TFT is a knowledge and task management framework for tiddlywiki. TFT short for time for task.

code: https://github.com/dongrentianyu/timefortask

demo: https://dongrentianyu.github.io/timefortask

依赖插件有："$:/plugins/kookma/shiraz", "$:/plugins/linonetwo/flow-chart", "$:/plugins/yaisog/taggingtree-filter", "$:/plugins/yaisog/tagstree-filter", "$:/plugins/linonetwo/in-tagtree-of", "$:/plugins/xp/aggregation",$:/plugins/Gk0Wk/echarts", "$:/plugins/linonetwo/super-tag"，如果CPL没有自动安装，请手动安装。

其中$:/plugins/xp/aggregation需要更新到0.5.0版本。

整体架构分成三部分。意义-任务-项目，通过字段`tft`来识别。

之前用的标签形式改成了用字段来处理。